function Start(idActorPlayer, idItem)
	--Hydra.ItemGiveToPlayer(idSelf, "QST_Hawe_S05_BrechtJournal")
	
	idActorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ElderLauBrechtA, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorClone) then
	    Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorClone, ElderLauBrechtB, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorClone, ElderLauBrechtB)
	    Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idActorClone)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	idActorCloneRitual = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ElderLauWitchwood, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorCloneRitual) then
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idActorCloneRitual, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Chant_Blessing_WaistLevel", false, true)
		Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(idActorCloneRitual, "RitualAltar01", idSelf) --show phased fx 01
		Hydra.QActorWait(idActorCloneRitual, 0.5, false)
		Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(idActorCloneRitual, "RitualAltar02", idSelf) --show phased fx 02
		Hydra.QActorWait(idActorCloneRitual, 1, false)
		--Hydra.QActorAnim(idActorCloneRitual, "GetHit_Back", false)
		Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(idActorCloneRitual, "RitualAltar03", idSelf) --show phased fx 03
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idActorCloneRitual, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Wounded", false)
		Hydra.QActorWait(idActorCloneRitual, 0.5, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorCloneRitual, ElderLauDying, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorCloneRitual, ElderLauDying)
		Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(idActorCloneRitual, "RitualAltarComplete", idSelf)
	    Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idActorCloneRitual, 0, ElderLauDying, false)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idActorCloneDying = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ElderLauDying, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorCloneDying) then
		Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idActorCloneDying, "AnimKey_Die", "AnimKey_Die_Loop", false)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorCloneDying, ElderLauCorpse)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idActorCloneDying, 0, ElderLauCorpse, false)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(convSick01A, idSelf, idActorSick01A)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idActorSick01B, convSick01A, true)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(convSick01B, idSelf, idActorSick01B, true)
end
